Package: text2data
Title: Convert Plain Text To Datasets
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Joe", "Ornstein", , "jornstein@uga.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-5704-2098"))
Description: A package for R users to interact with OpenAI's GPT-3 Python module. Includes handy functions for classifying texts according to user-defined functions, as well as converting plain text into structured datasets.
